{"tid":718067,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【槍擊爭產】身世曝光︰女疑犯做保鑣 曾受軍事訓練","createTime":"2018-06-26T13:31:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-26T13:58:52.000Z","uid":51271,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"96338cde94334d40ab58d926734dd1d8b92bfe5d","tid":718067,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T13:31:56.000Z","msg":"太古城下午發生爭產槍擊案，44歲姓詹女子涉嫌向舅父阿姨開槍，大姨送院後證實不治。詹女任職保鑣，是香港一間保鑣公司的負責人之一，亦是行內少數的女保鑣。詹女去年接受傳媒訪問時透露(相關連結︰<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2IsyIfK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2IsyIfK&d=aSudrojFQ0lCV3FZcZzkFcmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=d2aafc8f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2IsyIfK</a>)，她有武術底子，曾在外國作軍事訓練，具有數年保護富豪政要的經驗。另外，她又指香港的保鑣全都是有人介紹才能入行，富豪聘請保鑣時，現場會有一名資深的體能教練，她直言「通常都係搏擊高手嚟，佢會喺旁邊即場揼你，試你識唔識還擊，睇你忍受嘅痛苦有幾多」。<br />\n<br />\n今年初，詹女前往國際保鑣協會位於菲律賓的中心，與11名男保鑣接受訓練，當時她手持長槍，表現自信，眼神凌厲，其中亦有相片拍到她戴住墨鏡，雙手持槍作射擊訓練。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180626/58367230\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180626%2F58367230&d=aSudrojFQ0lCV3FZcZzkFcmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=151a7aef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180626%2F58367230&h=be3ab3cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180626/58367230</a>"},{"pid":"761cdcfb9564d9bb06ff98e7a5e8e16a6a1c1ac1","tid":718067,"uid":125752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96338cde94334d40ab58d926734dd1d8b92bfe5d","tid":718067,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T13:31:56.000Z","msg":"太古城下午發生爭產槍擊案，44歲姓詹女子涉嫌向舅父阿姨開槍，大姨送院後證實不治。詹女任職保鑣，是香港一間保鑣公司的負責人之一，亦是行內少數的女保鑣。詹女去年接受傳媒訪問時透露(相關連結︰<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2IsyIfK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2IsyIfK&d=aSudrojFQ0lCV3FZcZzkFcmDuOf2Rd%2